<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.4">
<l>vāṉavar tāmmakiḻa vaṉcaka ṭammuruḷa vañcamu laippēyiṉ nañcama tuṇṭavaṉē</l>
<l>kāṉaka valviḷaviṉ kāyuti rakkarutik kaṉṟatu koṇṭeṟiyum karuniṟa veṉkaṉṟē</l>
<l>tēṉuka ṉummuraṉum tiṇṭiṟal vennaraka ṉeṉpavar tāmmaṭiyacceruvati raccellu</l>
<l>māṉaiye ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who drank that poison from the deceitful demoness’s breast</l>
<l rend="indent"> and overtuned the strong cart so that the celestials rejoiced!</l>
<l>My little calf of dark complexion who,</l>
<l rend="indent">intending to drop the hard, unripe fruit of the wood-apple tree in the forest,</l>
<l rend="indent">grasped a calf and threw it!</l>
<l>Elephant who goes into battle while shaking so that those [demons]</l>
<l rend="indent">called Dhenuka, Mura, and valorious, cruel Naraka bend,</l>
<l>dance one time for me! Fighting bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
